This collection of scripts is designed to help create and administer rotas for staff

rota.csv shows the format for a sample rota.

The first line has a list of the staff members
The second line has a list of shiftpatterns, start times and length in hours and minutes of each pattern
The following lines contain rota shifts - day of week, date, name of shift pattern. 

rota2ics.pl produces from a provided cvs file similar to the provided rota.cvs sample ics and individual cvs files. 

